#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:177
msgid "Pay {priceStr}"
msgstr "{priceStr} を支払う"

#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:187
msgid "Payment required to confirm your spot"
msgstr "スポットを確定するには支払いが必要です"

#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:259
msgid "Pending approval"
msgstr "承認待ち"

#: src/components/organisms/ProfileModal.re.mjs:397
msgid "Prefer not to say"
msgstr "回答しない"

#: src/components/organisms/ProfileModal.re.mjs:429
msgid "Save & Join Event"
msgstr "保存して参加する"

#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:509
msgid ""
"There are players on the waitlist. If you leave, your spot will be given to "
"the next person. Are you sure?"
msgstr ""
"キャンセル待ちのプレイヤーがいます。退出すると、あなたの枠は次の人に渡されま"
"す。よろしいですか？"

#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:195
msgid ""
"This is a deposit hold only — payment is due to the organizer at the event. "
"The hold will be released after the event."
msgstr ""
"これはデポジットの仮押さえのみです — 支払いはイベント当日に主催者へ行ってくだ"
"さい。仮押さえはイベント終了後に解除されます。"

#: src/components/organisms/ProfileModal.re.mjs:278
msgid "This is how others will see you"
msgstr "他の人に表示される名前です"

#: src/components/organisms/ProfileModal.re.mjs:339
msgid "We need a few details before you can join this event"
msgstr "イベント参加に必要な情報を入力してください"

#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:273
msgid "Withdraw RSVP"
msgstr "参加登録を取り消す"

#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:273
msgid "Withdrawing..."
msgstr "取り消し中..."

#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:361
msgid "You're in"
msgstr "参加済み"

#: src/components/organisms/EventStickyFooter.re.mjs:263
msgid "Your RSVP is awaiting admin approval"
msgstr "あなたの参加登録は管理者の承認待ちです"

